kde-desktop-background-libvisual (1.1.6-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Replace blocking pa_simple + QTimer with async pa_threaded_mainloop /
    pa_stream callback pipeline; no more QTimer-driven audio polling
  * Replace pactl subprocess device enumeration with native
    pa_context_get_source_info_list(); monitor sources filtered via
    monitor_of_sink field — works transparently under PipeWire
  * Drop libpulse-simple linkage (pa_simple API no longer used)
  * Add SVG stock icon installed to hicolor/scalable/apps with component ID
    as filename; wire into AppStream metainfo and wallpaper metadata.json
  * Update documentation: PipeWire compat section, async backend architecture
    reference, debian/README.Debian notes on pipewire-pulse
  * Fix diagnostics.sh PROJECT_ROOT derivation for bare-filename invocation

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Thu, 15 May 2026 23:59:00 +0200

kde-desktop-background-libvisual (1.1.5-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Implement all 19 visualization types (Circular Spectrum, Plasma, Starfield,
    Fireworks, Matrix Rain, DNA Helix, Particle Storm, Ripple Effect,
    Tunnel Vision, Spiral Galaxy, Lightning, Geometric Dance, Audio Bars 3D,
    Kaleidoscope) — no more "Not Yet Implemented" placeholder
  * Config preview widget now shows a unique animated mini-preview for every
    visualization type, updating live as the user changes the selection
  * Audio device combo now enumerates only capture/microphone sources via
    pactl, filtering out monitor loopbacks; shows human-readable descriptions
  * Audio level indicator in config dialog is now driven by the real
    AudioVisualizer backend (was a sine-wave simulation); reports -60 dB
    when no microphone is connected to the selected device
  * Fix setAudioSource() to properly reconnect PulseAudio when device changes
  * Fix cfg_audioDevice to store PA source name, not display text

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Fri, 15 May 2026 21:21:41 +0200

